{
  "texts": [
    "Tables 3, 4 show the obtained Dice scores then training the segmentation networks with different combinations of real and synthetic images, and testing with real images, for BraTS 2020 and BraTS 2021 respectively.",
    "To make it easier to compare the performance to only using real images, Table 5 shows the relative Dice scores, i.e.",
    "the obtained mean Dice score when using real and synthetic images, or only synthetic images, divided by the obtained mean Dice score when using only real images (with augmentation).",
    "For U-Net trained with BraTS 2020 the diffusion model results in the highest Dice scores when using only synthetic images and augmentation, followed by StyleGAN 2, StyleGAN 3 and progressive GAN.",
    "A similar ranking is obtained for the Swin transformer."
  ]
}